1
00:00:04,958 --> 00:00:06,833
<i>- This is a dangerous move.</i>

2
00:00:06,916 --> 00:00:09,791
<i>I want to emphasize that.</i>

3
00:00:09,875 --> 00:00:13,625
If anything were to go wrong,
well...

4
00:00:13,708 --> 00:00:16,541
- Yeah, all or nothing.

5
00:00:16,625 --> 00:00:18,750
I get it.

6
00:00:18,833 --> 00:00:20,916
I've talked it over a bunch
with my mom and dad,

7
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:25,500
and I can't just give up.

8
00:00:25,583 --> 00:00:29,000
The surgery,
I want to have it.

